About this item

  • ILLUMINATE YOUR HOME - Transform your home into a vibrant oasis! Our smart bulb offers a wide range of beautiful shades with warm & cool white light options. With a lifespan of 25,000 hours & 800 lumens, create the perfect ambiance for any occasion.
  • HANDS-FREE CONTROL WITH ALEXA - Take control with voice commands through Alexa. Easily turn the smart light bulbs on and off, adjust brightness, and choose from a wide range of preset colors. Enjoy the convenience of hands-free lighting control
  • EASY SETUP, SCAN TO CONNECT - Setting up our colour changing light bulb with Alexa is a breeze. Alexa instantly pairs with the smart bulb upon installation. Just scan & connect. NOTE: Alexa device has to be connected to your 2.4 GHz WIFI channel.
  • CUSTOMIZE LIGHTING SCENES - Group multiple smart bulbs for synchronized lighting effects with a single command! Wake up to a gentle sunrise glow or set the light for a cozy movie night. You can also schedule lights to turn on & off at specific times!
  • WARRANTY AND CERTIFICATIONS - Our alexa light bulbs are ETL, FCC AC7Z-ESP868505 & ISED 32592-EA-9000 certified, ensuring their quality, safety compliance & efficiency. This product is under a 1-year warranty from the date of purchase and includes an English installation manual.

Product guides and documents

User Manual (PDF)

Product description

Illuminate your home with vibrant and versatile WiFi LED smart light bulbs. Our innovative smart bulbs offer a wide range of beautiful shades, including warm and cool white light options, allowing you to create the perfect ambiance for any occasion.

Setting up our color-changing light bulb with Alexa is a breeze. Simply scan and connect, and Alexa instantly pairs with the smart bulb upon installation. No complicated processes or technical expertise is required. Note: Ensure your Alexa device is connected to your 2.4 GHz WIFI channel for seamless connectivity.

Take control of your lighting with ease using voice commands through Alexa. From turning the smart bulb on and off to adjusting the brightness and choosing from a wide range of preset colors, enjoy the convenience of hands-free lighting control. Whether you want to set a relaxing mood or create a lively atmosphere, our smart light bulbs put the power in your voice.

With the ability to group multiple smart bulbs, you can create synchronized lighting effects with a single command. Create a gentle sunrise glow to wake up or set the perfect lighting for a cozy movie night. You can even schedule your lights to turn on and off automatically at specific times, adding a touch of automation to your daily routine.

Rest assured knowing that our alexa light bulbs meet the highest quality standards. It is ETL, FCC, and ISED certified, guaranteeing its safety, efficiency, and compliance with regulations. We also offer a 1-year warranty from the date of purchase, providing you with peace of mind.

It's time to make a smart choice for your home. Illuminate your space with style and convenience with Evolux by Lloyd's Wi-Fi LED Smart Bulb.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzes reviews to verify trustworthiness.

5 out of 5 stars
The easiest device to set up
I've used smart devices (smart plugs and lightbulbs); this one is by far the easiest to set up: just install it and turn on, wait for it to finish flashing (for 30 sec?), then launch Alexa app on phone, then it is set up automatically and ready to use - this was totally unexpectedly easy;the other 2 smart lightbulb brands I had tried previously all need to turn on / off power multiple times then set it up in their own apps which could take several minutes.I bought this bundled with Echo Pop during black friday sales and tbh did not expect it to work this fast given some negative reviews and my past experience using other brands.I do not know if it's a new implementation / upgrade of all smart devices and I'm not sure if other brands all have this easy setup at the time of this review; just saying I'm really impressed how easy the installation was.

  • Chit
    4.0 out of 5 stars It actually works
    Reviewed in Canada on November 27, 2022
    Number of Items: 1Verified Purchase
    Ok, it is my first Alexa smart led bulb which actually works.
    What is great:
    - It works
    - WIFI integration is quite reliable. It works in areas where other lights failed due to weak wifi - 5 stars here.
    - White is good 800lm
    - nice manual
    What is not so good:
    - as expected, color lights are not so strong, but this issue is present on other lights as well.
    - Issue in Alexa - Alexa doesn't allow to connect with wifi6 network with PMF. Disable PMF and connect, then switch PMF to optional and it will work. However, WPA3 is not supported as well.
    - Alexa installation could be simpler.
    - Dimming function is not uniform

    I can recommend this light bulb if you have Alexa or weak wifi. No regret on my side.
